snippet.title: Understanding Microsoft Agents | EP05
snippet.description:
In this session, you'll learn how the Employee Self-Service Agent in M365 Copilot serves as your single front door for HR and IT support - giving you a jump start in building an agent with preconfigured workflows and templates that work with existing systems such as ServiceNow, Workday, and SAP SuccessFactors.

Watch the other Understanding Agents sessions here: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLi9EhCY4z99X74gEXX6HXTjZfxAlbjIJf
